Detailed Description

template<class T>
class gaia::base::HashSet< T >::const_iterator

Implements const iterator for hashset.

Hashset con_iterator is only used to traverse.

 // Creates a hashset and adds serveral datum.
 HashSet<size_t> hs;
 for (size_t i = 0; i < 50; i++) {
      hs.add(i);
 }
 
 // Creates an iterator for hashset.
 HashSet<size_t>::const_iterator citer;
 
 // Travese hashset
 size_t sum = 0;
 for (citer = hs.begin(); citer != hs.end(); citer++) {
      sum += *citer;
 }
